Surf_shoria 

by razer with the help of Mark_c.

Thanks to all the people who beta tested the map for me, I really appreciate you taking the time to help me out. 
The idea of this map was really to round up all the stages I have made, that never got used for their intended purpose. Also made a few new stuff and remade an old stage as a bonus. 

Hopefully you'll enjoy it :)
